{
  "stem": "18665.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 287.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people who lived outside, prior to that, who had businesses, had to either close them and move into the, into the ghetto area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there we stayed until the end of the war, until 1945.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's when life was difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During that period, during the occupation of the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Japanese immediately occupied the whole city, walked across Garden Bridge and occupied Frenchtown and total city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were, they were in charge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- there were American gunboats in the harbor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe, I believe the name of one was the Wakefield.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they sank themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One ship, I think, escaped, a British ship, I believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very swift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Japanese moved right in the next morning, it was all apparently pre-planned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- all the British, American, and the ABC, all the Dutch and the French, and all the aliens were eventually rounded up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had to wear armbands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we could still-- actually, in '41, we was-- '42, we're still able to go into the city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then eventually, when barbed wire was put around the district, unless you had a permit and you had to go to a police station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The man in charge of that police station was-- his name was Ghoya.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Very much feared by the immigrants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He called himself the King of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was a little man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if he didn't like your face, he wouldn't give you a permit to go into the city, because some people had jobs outside of the district and needed to go there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or if you were a particularly tall person, he would jump up on a chair and slap you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a inferiority complex, the man.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
